<string>This open-source software is a content-based similar case retrieval tool for medical imaging. By constructing a medical image vector store, particularly empowered by domain-specific self-supervised pretrained visual extractors, it enables more accurate clinical similar case lookup, covering application scenarios including difficult case consultation reference, follow-up lesion dynamic tracking, and typical case retrieval for teaching and research.
</string>     </property>
